arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDFZNNH4TCVCNPISOVGY6B5H7FQ.jpg&h=b18df599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張崑陽：扼殺議會不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n有份參與初選、現正流亡海外的張崑陽在網上發文，指否決《財政預算案》一直被建制派抹黑為違法行為，強調這是立會議員根據《基本法》獲賦予的權利，「完全談不上顛覆之有」。他認為昨日大清算反映未來任何議會不合作運動在港共政權眼中都可以是顛覆行為，證明立會如同人大和政協般只是橡皮圖章。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織民權觀察強調，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sUMaAPGWJN0RsKq7ecoNtnuNx3E=/1600x4158/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ILQHKXJUVJB2HPL7MZFVNHIUCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsUMaAPGWJN0RsKq7ecoNtnuNx3E%3D%2F1600x4158%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FILQHKXJUVJB2HPL7MZFVNHIUCE.jpg&h=e82c834f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QEjzM985_C25gn8ACGO8zDXgxiQ=/1600x3102/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N7CH3BXPL5BX7PN2J5KGSKGIBE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQEjzM985_C25gn8ACGO8zDXgxiQ%3D%2F1600x3102%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN7CH3BXPL5BX7PN2J5KGSKGIBE.JPG&h=788747b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"攬炒變自炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b984c5264e7076cedc001253fdeeff92d8c1923a","tid":2357291,"uid":5674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒10部有中共加速之下<br />\n由第一部dq加國安法，一跳就跳左去第十部<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada85b443b815923baf0af8d129271848eeb1fdf","tid":2357291,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T